  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个部署流程的时序图，场景是swaparoo系统启动基础设施并邀请投票者加入。核心角色有Voter1、swaparoo的部署器Core、Zoe协调器，还有swaparoo的委员会Ctee。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Voter1",
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "swaparoo"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我注意到Core的标注是\"swaparoo<brdeployer\"，Ctee是\"swaparoo<brcommittee\"，这种换行标注需要保留吗？另外启动流程是从Core发起吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Ctee",
        "swaparoo"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，保留换行标注。流程是Core先调用Zoe的startInstance来启动Redis缓存，然后Zoe让Ctee启动Etcd集群，Ctee返回WorkerNode给Zoe，Zoe再把Redis缓存实例返回给Core。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，前四步消息已经画好：Core到Zoe的startInstance，Zoe到Ctee的start，Ctee返回WorkerNode，Zoe返回Redis缓存。接下来Core要做什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来Core要向Ctee查询投票邀请，具体是调用E(Infra_RedisCache).getVoterInvitations，传入IngressController作为参数。Ctee返回WorkerNode列表后，Core最后给Voter1发送invitationV1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Ctee",
        "Voter1",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "invitationV1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Core到Ctee的消息是\"E(Infra_RedisCache).getVoterInvitations(Infra_IngressController)\"，然后Ctee返回[Infra_WorkerNode]，最后Core到Voter1是\"invitationV1\"。这些消息类型混用没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Ctee",
        "Voter1",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "invitationV1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，方法调用、数组、简单消息都有是合理的。对了，第一步Core到Zoe用虚线箭头表示异步调用，其他返回消息也用虚线，但Core到Ctee的查询用实线箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "发现个问题：我注意到第三步Ctee返回给Zoe的消息写的是\"{Infra_WorkerNode}\"，但第五步Ctee返回给Core的是\"[Infra_WorkerNode]\"，花括号和方括号需要统一吗？还是故意区分对象和数组？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ctee",
        "Zoe",
        "Core",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保持原样，这是故意的——Ctee给Zoe的是单节点对象，给Core的是节点数组。另外开启自动编号， actor Voter1用别名显示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Voter1",
        "autonumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。时序图已按你的要求绘制：Voter1作为actor，Core、Zoe、Ctee四个参与者，七步消息流，自动编号，箭头类型区分同步异步，消息格式保留对象、数组、方法调用三种形式。",
